Prediction: The predicted melting point of lomefloxacin taking into account the given functional groups effects would be approximately 180 (quinolone base) + 30 (first fluorine) + 30 (second fluorine) + 0 (piperazinyl group neutral effect) + 5 (methyl group on piperazine) + 50 (carboxylic acid group) = 295 degrees.
